'''''Hawkeye''''' was a [[DP20 gunship/Legends|Corellian Gunship]] used by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]]. It accompanied the cruiser [[Liberty/Legends|''Liberty'']] on a number of occasions, at times when ''Liberty'' was not operating alone.

